      <title>瑞秋·里夫斯的英国增税预算中值得关注的事情</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/uk-budget-2024-what-to-look-for-in-rachel-reeves-announcements</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雷切尔·里夫斯给自己设定了看似矛盾的任务：结束公共服务紧缩政策、促进增长和实现财政稳定，以向市场保证工党是值得信赖的，可以管理英国的财政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/uk-budget-2024-what-to-look-for-in-rachel-reeves-announcements</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 12:08:51 GMT</pubDate>
