    <item>
      <title>GSK 与中国生物科技公司签署高达 8.5 亿美元的狼疮治疗协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/gsk-inks-lupus-deal-with-chinese-biotech-for-up-to-850-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葛兰素史克公司 (GSK Plc) 以高达 8.5 亿美元的价格从中国生物科技公司 Chimagen Biosciences 收购了一种实验性药物，增强了这家英国制药商治疗狼疮的潜在药物阵容。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/gsk-inks-lupus-deal-with-chinese-biotech-for-up-to-850-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黑石集团新直接贷款基金募集 220 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/blackstone-raises-22-billion-in-new-direct-lending-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社看到的一份声明显示，黑石公司为针对机构投资者的新直接贷款基金筹集了约 220 亿美元的资金，包括预期杠杆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/blackstone-raises-22-billion-in-new-direct-lending-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
